##  Compiz standalone with a bottom bar conky wih mpd and gmail   ##
####################################################################

Very simple conky easy to setup just place the folder named "conky" at your home and launch 
"conky -c ~/conky/gnome/conkyrc"
Inside "extras" is the wallpaper

